QuestData.Title: Meet Me at Triumph
QuestData.Description: Thanks in part to your efforts, we've stabilized the situation here. We need to turn our attention south, to Fort Triumph.$B$BFort Triumph is the keystone of our operation in the Barrens - the vital land-link between Northwatch and Theramore.$B$BI'll pack up and head out separately. Report to Commander Roberts at the fortress and I will see you there soon. Together, we will secure the frontier!
QuestData.LogDescription: Report to Commander Roberts at Fort Triumph in Southern Barrens.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Report to Commander Roberts at Fort Triumph in Southern Barrens.
QuestData.RewardText: Have you heard? The General never made it!$B$BKilled in the field, like some kind of dog!
